node.text: Join Julien’s Auctions on Friday, November 30th and Saturday, December 1st in Los Angeles and live online at Julien's Live for our "Property From The Collection of Hugh M. Hefner" auction as we celebrate the pop culture icon and publishing giant who introduced the world to the legendary Playboy brand. All proceeds of the sale will benefit The Hugh M. Hefner Foundation in support of organizations that advocate for and defend civil rights, with special emphasis on First Amendment rights and rational sex and drug policies since 1964.

node.title: Julien’s Auctions: Property From The Collection of Hugh M. Hefner

node.text:
Cruise Day 4 @nourelnil ⛵️ ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Gebel Silsileh. Here, the Nile, flowing between two mountains ranges, is at its narrowest. We were one of the few visitors at this site today. We visited the small temple of Horemheb and walked through the sandstone quarries, where ancient Egyptians cut stone for many of their most famous temples. The views of the Nile from here are so picturesque and this whole trip has felt like being in a dream. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Video: @jeremybrookover⁣⁣
Guide: @adelonline73⁣⁣
⁣
#egypt #nourelnil #nileriver #luxor #nile #crystalhefner #passionpassport #beautifuldestinations #love #adventure #travelmore #travel #wanderlust #explore #quarry #temple #gebelsilsileh #aswan⁣

node.text:
We walked through sandstone quarries after visiting the small temple of Horemheb. The quarry is where ancient Egyptians cut stone for many of their most famous temples. It was so amazing to see where the rocks started off in some of the incredible places we’ve visited between Luxor and Aswan. We loved learning how they were cut and transported and how truly advanced the ancient Egyptian people were. ⁣
⁣
⁣
Location: @nourelnil⁣
Guide: @adelonline73⁣
Photos: @ryanmalaty ⁣
⁣
#quarry #aswan #thisisegypt #rock #templerock #love #travel #igtravel #nourelnil #crystalhefner #travelmore #passionpassport #beautifuldestinations

node.text:
Nile cruise Day 3 with @nourelnil ⛵️ 

This is a day devoted to the river. We had breakfast and set sail. We stopped at an island and had the chance to enjoy ourselves on our boat, Adelaïde. Someone on the boat had a birthday so we celebrated them and then tied up at the foot of floodlit temple of Gebel Silsileh.

🎥 @jeremybrookover

node.text:
Nile cruise Day 2 with @nourelnil ⛵️ ⁣
⁣
El Kab, on the East bank of the Nile, was once the capital of Upper Egypt and is still home to the temple of Nekhbet, as well as a row of fascinating decorated tombs carved into the slope of the mountains. We walked through a small fisherman village to get to El Kab. ⁣
⁣
In the afternoon, we visited Edfu, home to the Greco-Roman temple dedicated to the god Horus. This is among the best preserved of all Egyptian temples 🇪🇬 ⁣
⁣
⁣
🎥 by the best: @jeremybrookover⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
#nourelnil #egypt #instatravel #igtravel #edfu #nekhbet #elkab #horus #adventure #travelmore #passionpassport #love #beautifuldestinations #paradise #votd #crystalhefner #nile #nilerivercruise #nileriver
